column.Name: CustomField1
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, CustomKey FROM iCustom1 div INNER JOIN fnx_Permissions_GetGuidProductTypePermissions('##TEAMID##', 26) access ON access.ProductTypeId = div.CustomID AND access.PermissionRoleID > 0 ORDER BY Custom

column.Name: StyleType
column.lookupquery: SELECT StyleTypeID, StyleTypeDescription FROM pStyleType ORDER BY StyleTypeOrder

column.Name: WorkflowType
column.lookupquery: SELECT WorkflowTemplateID, TemplateName FROM pWorkflowTemplate WHERE Active = 1 AND Body = 0 ORDER BY TemplateName

column.Name: CustomField2
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, CustomSort FROM iCustom2 Where CustomSort = 2 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: WashType
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM iCustom14 ORDER BY Custom

column.Name: StyleSet
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, CustomKey FROM xCustom9 ORDER BY Custom

column.Name: CustomField3
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom FROM aCustom3 Where CustomSort1 = 5 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: StyleCategory
column.lookupquery: SELECT StyleCategoryId, StyleCategory, StyleCategorySort FROM pStyleCategory Where StyleCategorySort = 40 ORDER BY StyleCategory

column.Name: CustomField4
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom FROM aCustom12 Where CustomRelationId = ##ID## ORDER BY Custom

column.Name: SizeRange
column.lookupquery: SELECT SizeRangeCode, CustomM FROM pSizeRange Where CustomM = 1 ORDER BY SizeRangeCode

column.Name: CustomField5
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM pSeason ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: SizeClass
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM pSizeClass ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: CustomField6
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM pYear ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: CustomField9
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom FROM xCustom29 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: CustomField12
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom1 FROM xCustom26 Where Custom1 = 1 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: CustomField11
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom FROM xCustom28 ORDER BY CustomKey

column.Name: Designer
column.lookupquery: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(ISNULL(FirstName, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(LastName, ''))) AS fullname from users Where TradePartner = 0 order by fullname
